        <updateDate>2021-05-10T16:54:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>David Dorn Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill increases criminal penalties for rioting and related acts, such as inciting or organizing a riot.</p> <p>Specifically, this bill increases the maximum term of imprisonment for such offenses from 5 to 10 years. Additionally, if a fine is imposed for an offense, the bill sets a minimum fine amount of $1,000.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
